<%= render "articles/embeds/competitor_section", competitor: "mbuzz", number: 2, title: "Best for Model Flexibility" %>

**Why consider mbuzz:** HockeyStack gives you one attribution view. mbuzz lets you compare 8 models side-by-side and build custom logic for B2B. *Disclosure: mbuzz is our product.*

Server-side tracking captures events on your backend — no ad blockers, no missing touches across long B2B buyer journeys. 7 attribution models for long sales cycles: compare First Touch, Last Touch, Markov Chain, Shapley Value, and more side-by-side. Custom attribution rules via DSL let you weight touchpoints by stage, channel, or engagement depth. LTV attribution tracks renewals and expansion back to acquisition source.

**10-minute setup** with native SDKs for [Rails](https://rubygems.org/gems/mbuzz), [Django](https://pypi.org/project/mbuzz), [Laravel](https://packagist.org/packages/mbuzz/mbuzz-php), and [Node.js](https://www.npmjs.com/package/mbuzz). Pricing: Free tier, then $29-299/mo (vs HockeyStack's $2,200+).

